horrid /ˈhɒrɪd/

1. ADJ If you describe something as horrid , you mean that it is extremely unpleasant. 极讨厌的 [非正式] 

例： What a horrid smell! 多么难闻的气味！ 

2. ADJ If you describe someone as horrid , you mean that they behave in a very unpleasant way toward other people. (人) 令人讨厌的 [非正式] 

例： I must have been a horrid little girl. 我以前一定是个招人讨厌的小女孩。

